statements.sql: select count(*) as aggregate from `users` left join `companies` on `users`.`company_id` = `companies`.`id` left join `user_divisions` on `users`.`user_division_id` = `user_divisions`.`id` left join `user_regions` on `users`.`user_region_id` = `user_regions`.`id` left join `user_locations` on `users`.`user_locations_id` = `user_locations`.`id` left join `users` as `parent` on `users`.`line_manager` = `parent`.`id` where not exists (select 1 from `role_user` left join `roles` on `role_user`.`role_id` = `roles`.`id` where role_user.user_id = users.id and `roles`.`name` = 'App version handling') and (`users`.`workshops_user_flag` = '0' or `users`.`workshops_user_flag` = '2') and (`users`.`is_disabled` = '0')

select `users`.`id`, `users`.`email`, `users`.`first_name`, `users`.`last_name`, `users`.`username`, `users`.`company_id`, `users`.`job_title`, `users`.`mobile`, `users`.`landline`, `users`.`is_disabled`, `users`.`enable_login`, `users`.`is_verified`, `users`.`engineer_id`, `users`.`imei`, `users`.`field_manager_phone`, `companies`.`name`, `users`.`created_at`, `users`.`updated_at`, `user_divisions`.`name` as `division_name`, `user_regions`.`name` as `region_name`, `user_locations`.`name` as `location_name`,  (CASE
WHEN LOCATE(';',users.user_agent) = 0 THEN null
ELSE SUBSTRING_INDEX(SUBSTRING_INDEX(users.user_agent, ';', 3), ';', -1)
END)
as app,  (CASE
WHEN LOCATE(';',users.user_agent) = 0 THEN null
ELSE SUBSTRING_INDEX(SUBSTRING_INDEX(users.user_agent, ';', 2), ';', -1)
END)
as device, CONCAT(parent.first_name, ' ', parent.last_name) as line_manager_name, (SELECT GROUP_CONCAT(r.name) FROM users u, roles r, role_user ur WHERE u.id=ur.user_id AND r.id = ur.role_id AND u.id=users.id) as userroles, DATE_FORMAT(CONVERT_TZ(users.last_login, 'UTC', 'Europe/London'),
'%H:%i:%s %d %b %Y') as 'last_login' from `users` left join `companies` on `users`.`company_id` = `companies`.`id` left join `user_divisions` on `users`.`user_division_id` = `user_divisions`.`id` left join `user_regions` on `users`.`user_region_id` = `user_regions`.`id` left join `user_locations` on `users`.`user_locations_id` = `user_locations`.`id` left join `users` as `parent` on `users`.`line_manager` = `parent`.`id` where not exists (select 1 from `role_user` left join `roles` on `role_user`.`role_id` = `roles`.`id` where role_user.user_id = users.id and `roles`.`name` = 'App version handling') and (`users`.`workshops_user_flag` = '0' or `users`.`workshops_user_flag` = '2') and (`users`.`is_disabled` = '0') and (`users`.`is_disabled` = '0') order by first_name ASC limit 20 offset 0
